    "description": "这是一场充满奇思妙想、荒诞鬼怪和高能武器的杀戮大冒险。要想完成这个大冒险，也许需要有一丁点儿的策略思维，以及一丁点儿的运气。如果遇到挫折，多试几次，合理配置手里的资源，也许会有解决的办法。当您不再满足目前的游戏难度时，记得在游戏开始前，适当调高怪物的数量，您会发现一个新的世界。<br>QQ：883417277<br><br>卡牌：击杀怪物有机率获得丰富的卡牌，抽取卡牌可随机获得武器、道具、被动技能等，让您随时充满战斗力。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343350/extras/a9c5028d92745489653b442852835ba3.poster.avif?t=1724346129\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343350/extras/a9c5028d92745489653b442852835ba3.webm?t=1724346129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343350/extras/a9c5028d92745489653b442852835ba3.mp4?t=1724346129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>AI队友：游戏里有多种不同类型、并拥有特殊技能的AI队友，找到并利用他们强大的能力，帮助您完成最终任务。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343350/extras/6696717b41c89b6d0e34b6279b59e258.poster.avif?t=1724346129\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343350/extras/6696717b41c89b6d0e34b6279b59e258.webm?t=1724346129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343350/extras/6696717b41c89b6d0e34b6279b59e258.mp4?t=1724346129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>小队模式：游戏中可随时进入到小队模式来编辑您的小队阵型或配置您拥有的卡牌，以便应对各种危险情况。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343350/extras/eef4c8765e9ecb21070e6134a2a788cf.poster.avif?t=1724346129\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343350/extras/eef4c8765e9ecb21070e6134a2a788cf.webm?t=1724346129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343350/extras/eef4c8765e9ecb21070e6134a2a788cf.mp4?t=1724346129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>探索：探索随机分布在地图里的房间，可获得丰厚的奖励，当然，在房间里也有东西等着您。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343350/extras/ce77bdeb9c13e542a7eee30d8bf0b0c5.poster.avif?t=1724346129\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343350/extras/ce77bdeb9c13e542a7eee30d8bf0b0c5.webm?t=1724346129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343350/extras/ce77bdeb9c13e542a7eee30d8bf0b0c5.mp4?t=1724346129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>怪物：十余种怪物在地图上随机生成，每种怪物都拥有特殊技能，您必须非常了解它们，否则随时会全军覆没。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343350/extras/2a842a3e5a670fd7a639e75d90eb6e31.poster.avif?t=1724346129\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343350/extras/2a842a3e5a670fd7a639e75d90eb6e31.webm?t=1724346129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343350/extras/2a842a3e5a670fd7a639e75d90eb6e31.mp4?t=1724346129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>守卫：成千上万的怪物会在最后发动总攻，您需要利用收集到的物资来对抗他们。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343350/extras/58fc8130d537828b76677261e4be5e5c.poster.avif?t=1724346129\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343350/extras/58fc8130d537828b76677261e4be5e5c.webm?t=1724346129\